<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 id="title">Rainy Day</h1>
  <p>Create a list of things you would like to do on a rainy day</p>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <% if !@current_user %>
    <div class="col-xs-4">
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-4">
      <%= link_to 'Login', '#login', class:'btn btn-primary main_btns', 
        data: {:toggle => 'modal'} %>
      <%= link_to 'About Us', '#about_us', class:'btn btn-primary main_btns' %>
      <%= link_to 'Sign Up', '#signup', class:'btn btn-primary main_btns', 
        data: {:toggle => 'modal'} %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-4">
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
<br>
<br>
<div id='use_cases'>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 use_case">
      <div class="thumbnail">
        <i class="fa fa-plane fa-5x"></i>
        <div class="caption">
          <h3>Search</h3>
          <p>Always wanted to explore your town, but feel like your too busy? 
            Save those trips for a rainy day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 use_case">
      <div class="thumbnail">
        <i class="fa fa-list fa-5x"></i>
        <div class="caption">
          <h3>Create a list</h3>
          <p>Selecting a destination and adding a goal to complete at that 
            destination will populate in your Goal page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 use_case">
      <div class="thumbnail">
        <i class="fa fa-trophy fa-5x"></i>
        <div class="caption">
          <h3>Achieve</h3>
          <p>Once you have completed a goal, it will populate into your 
            achievements page where you can view all of your accomplishments</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
